3. cs.LO (Computer Science and Logic in Computer Science) is also likely as the paper deals with formal verification of game properties. 
4. cs.AI (Computer Science and Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper discusses optimal strategies for players. 
5. cs.PL (Computer Science and Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper discusses the computation of winning sets using algorithms.
